24:44.240 --> 24:48.240
but if he is a Muslim, they don’t live like ascetics in young age.

24:48.400 --> 24:51.160
They enjoy life and in old age they are satisfied souls.

24:51.320 --> 24:56.320
So you better talk to a Muslim old man than to an Hindu old man.”

24:57.040 --> 25:00.480
I mean the reading is so correct about things, you know.

25:01.160 --> 25:08.040
Everything that he said was so practical and so sensible.

25:08.280 --> 25:11.560
I was really surprised how he could say these things

25:11.680 --> 25:15.400
with such sweetness and with such goodness

25:16.000 --> 25:18.440
and how he understood so many things so well.

25:18.640 --> 25:23.520
And he was a very young fellow; about I would say

25:23.680 --> 25:25.560
thirty to thirty two years of age.

25:26.000 --> 25:31.440
So he came to Bombay to see us.

25:32.160 --> 25:35.040
He didn’t know our full address, he only knew Marine Drive

25:35.320 --> 25:39.080
so he told the fellow his taxi fellow “You drive me at Marine Drive “.

25:39.280 --> 25:41.200
He said ” Marine Drive is a big place”.

25:41.360 --> 25:43.320
He said “You drive me anywhere in Marine Drive “, so he drove.

25:43.480 --> 25:46.240
So he went and asked “Is there a very tall

25:46.440 --> 25:49.280
