25:57.440 --> 25:59.600
He said “Just one tall is staying there, you see”.

26:00.040 --> 26:03.040
So that’s how he came to our house. And he showed them  his shoes,

26:03.200 --> 26:06.040
This shoe is given to me by my sahib, he is also very tall, you see.

26:06.280 --> 26:10.320
So he said “This shoe he has given me and he wears the same style of shoes”.

26:10.640 --> 26:13.640
So servants notice all these things, they are very practical people.

26:14.160 --> 26:17.600
So another gardener who met him, he said “Yes there’s a tall fellow

26:18.040 --> 26:21.240
and he wears the same type of shoes”. And so he came to our house.

26:22.040 --> 26:26.040
How they are sharp and how their eyes are so

26:26.320 --> 26:30.080
penetrating, how they know everything about everything.

26:32.120 --> 26:35.480
It is remarkable, very remarkable

26:36.080 --> 26:38.000
and that is what we have to be.

26:38.240 --> 26:44.040
We have tobe gurus with the Mother’s  influence on us,

26:44.280 --> 26:47.160
